Name: Over My Dead Pixel
About the game: Over My Dead Pixel is a top down shooter where you command antivirus software to defend your computer from malware. Beware, firing your weapons will shrink your playspace. Acquire powerups and modules to unleash a torrent of attacks. Maneuver deftly to avoid the enemies and the walls, as one single hit means restarting. UNLEASH A TORRENT OF PIXELS UPDATE YOUR ABILITIES EXECUTE MALWARE UNLOCK COLOR PALETTES SURGE UP THE LEADERBOARDS BUT ABOVE ALL ELSE SECURE YOUR DATA WILL YOU MAKE IT? OVER MY DEAD PIXEL
